Feature:
  Agile Story: 9
  "9. As a user, I should be able to use ""Filter
  and search"" functionality on Active Stream."

  Scenario:1. User should be able to search by clicking on default filters. (work, favorate, my activity, annoucements, and workflows)

  Scenario:2. User should be able to search by selecting Date, Type, Author, To and more default dropdowns.

  Scenario:3. User should be able to type-in keyword to search previous posts.

  Scenario:4. User should be able to use Save Filter functionality on search bar. "